  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stream Avatars</strong> is an interactive overlay for live broadcasters on <strong>Twitch, Facebook, Youtube, Trovo, Kick, and Dlive</strong>. It even works with multiple services at the same time! Your viewers can knock each other off the screen with <strong>punches, bombs</strong>, or a<strong> duel show match</strong> where the winner takes all!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/726848eae565f54438b9492fa88cd130.poster.avif?t=1758468867\" width=628 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/726848eae565f54438b9492fa88cd130.webm?t=1758468867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/726848eae565f54438b9492fa88cd130.mp4?t=1758468867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/ba1a5a9f03544586bfe41742e572e518.poster.avif?t=1758468867\" width=627 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/ba1a5a9f03544586bfe41742e572e518.webm?t=1758468867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unleash Your Creativity! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can create your own avatars, equipment, and name tags to fit the theme of your stream. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If creativity is not your strong suit, download some community-made Avatars from the Steam workshop! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Currency Integrations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mixitup, Streamlabs, & Stream Elements</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disclaimers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you use a dual PC setup? - If you do, you might need to get Stream Avatars on a secondary steam account for the streaming machine instead of your primary steam account! Family Sharing is not possible for Software on steam* </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mac OSX Must use an integration in window settings called \"Syphon\", or use window captures with chromakeying out the background.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Support / Help</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-If searching the documentation site doesn't help, Feel free to visit the discord for help with any issues you might be having.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Commands: After you connect, Type: !commands </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stream Avatars</strong> is an interactive overlay for live broadcasters on <strong>Twitch, Facebook, Youtube, Trovo, Kick, and Dlive</strong>. It even works with multiple services at the same time! Your viewers can knock each other off the screen with <strong>punches, bombs</strong>, or a<strong> duel show match</strong> where the winner takes all!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/726848eae565f54438b9492fa88cd130.poster.avif?t=1758468867\" width=628 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/726848eae565f54438b9492fa88cd130.webm?t=1758468867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/726848eae565f54438b9492fa88cd130.mp4?t=1758468867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/ba1a5a9f03544586bfe41742e572e518.poster.avif?t=1758468867\" width=627 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/665300/extras/ba1a5a9f03544586bfe41742e572e518.webm?t=1758468867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unleash Your Creativity! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can create your own avatars, equipment, and name tags to fit the theme of your stream. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If creativity is not your strong suit, download some community-made Avatars from the Steam workshop! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Currency Integrations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mixitup, Streamlabs, & Stream Elements</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disclaimers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you use a dual PC setup? - If you do, you might need to get Stream Avatars on a secondary steam account for the streaming machine instead of your primary steam account! Family Sharing is not possible for Software on steam* </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mac OSX Must use an integration in window settings called \"Syphon\", or use window captures with chromakeying out the background.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Support / Help</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-If searching the documentation site doesn't help, Feel free to visit the discord for help with any issues you might be having.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Commands: After you connect, Type: !commands </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
